</header><div class="entry-content">
<p class="has-medium-font-size">This <strong>Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake</strong> is rich, fudgy, and ready in just 1 minute. Packed with 32 grams protein and simple ingredients, it's the perfect quick dessert or snack when chocolate cravings hit.</p>



<p>Microwave it for speed or bake it in the oven for a traditional texture. Either way, it's moist, satisfying, and easy to customize with your favorite add-ins. If you want to boost your protein even more, try topping it with my protein whipped cream!</p>



<p>Time to make this rich, high-protein chocolate brownie mug cake-here's the simple step-by-step:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" fetchpriority="high" src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-1200x1200.jpg" alt="Close-up of a rich, fudgy Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake in a mug, topped with chocolate chips, ready to eat." data-skip-lazy class="wp-image-2586" srcset="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1.jpg 1200w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-500x500.jpg 500w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-720x720.jpg 720w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-360x360.jpg 360w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-180x180.jpg 180w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-snippet wprm-recipe-template-snippet-basic"><a href="#recipe" data-recipe="2576" style="color: #333333;" class="wprm-recipe-jump wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal">Jump to Recipe</a> - <a href="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wprm_print/protein-chocolate-brownie-mug-cake" style="color: #333333;" class="wprm-recipe-print wprm-recipe-link wprm-print-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal" data-recipe-id="2576" data-template="" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Print Recipe</a></div></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-make-mug-cakes-with-protein-powder"><strong>Ingredients</strong></h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Dry Ingredients</strong></h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>¼ cup (30g) chocolate protein powder</li>



<li>1 tablespoon all-purpose or oat flour</li>



<li>1 tablespoon sugar or sweetener of choice</li>



<li>1 tablespoon cocoa powder</li>



<li>½ teaspoon baking powder</li>



<li>A pinch of salt</li>



<li>1 ½ tablespoon chocolate chips (optional)</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Wet Ingredients</strong></h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>3 tablespoon thick Greek yogurt (egg-free recipe)</li>



<li>3 tablespoon milk or any milk alternative</li>



<li>1 teaspoon olive oil or coconut oil</li>



<li>½ teaspoon vanilla extract</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Optional Add-Ins</strong></h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>White chocolate chips or cocoa nibs</li>



<li>Mini marshmallows</li>



<li>Peanut butter, almond butter, or other nut butters</li>



<li>Espresso or instant coffee powder (¼-½ tsp)</li>



<li>Toffee bits or caramel chips</li>
</ul>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Side-by-side comparison of Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cakes—microwaved in a mug and oven-baked in a ramekin—showing the difference in texture and appearance." class="wp-image-2587" data-lazy-srcset="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie.jpg 1200w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-300x300.jpg 300w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-150x150.jpg 150w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-768x768.jpg 768w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-500x500.jpg 500w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-96x96.jpg 96w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-1200x1200.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-1200x1200.jpg" alt="Side-by-side comparison of Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cakes—microwaved in a mug and oven-baked in a ramekin—showing the difference in texture and appearance." class="wp-image-2587" srcset="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie.jpg 1200w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-300x300.jpg 300w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-150x150.jpg 150w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-768x768.jpg 768w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-500x500.jpg 500w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/How-to-make-a-protein-brownie-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ingredients"><strong><br><br>How to Make Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake</strong></h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Microwave Method (Quick &amp; Easy):</strong></h3>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Mix all dry ingredients in a mug.</li>



<li>Stir in wet ingredients until smooth.</li>



<li>Microwave for 60 seconds. If not set, continue in 10-second bursts (up to 90 sec).</li>



<li>Cool for 1-2 minutes and enjoy warm.</li>
</ol>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Oven Method (Optional):</strong></h3>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).</li>



<li>Mix everything in an oven-safe ramekin.</li>



<li>Bake for 10 minutes, or until set.</li>
</ol>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Warm, high-protein chocolate brownie mug cake in a ceramic mug, garnished with a drizzle of chocolate and ready to enjoy." class="wp-image-2585" data-lazy-srcset="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1200x1200.jpg 1200w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-300x300.jpg 300w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-150x150.jpg 150w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-768x768.jpg 768w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake.jpg 2048w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-500x500.jpg 500w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-96x96.jpg 96w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1200x1200.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1200x1200.jpg" alt="Warm, high-protein chocolate brownie mug cake in a ceramic mug, garnished with a drizzle of chocolate and ready to enjoy." class="wp-image-2585" srcset="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1200x1200.jpg 1200w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-300x300.jpg 300w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-150x150.jpg 150w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-768x768.jpg 768w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake.jpg 2048w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-500x500.jpg 500w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Protein-Brownie-Mug-Cake-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<p>If you enjoyed this Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake, you might also like my <a href="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/high-calorie-high-protein-chocolate-peanut-butter-smoothie/">High Calorie High Protein Chocolate Peanut Butter Smoothie</a> for a creamy protein boost, or my <a href="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/protein-coffee/">Protein Coffee (Proffee Recipe)</a> to start your day with a delicious, energizing drink. Both are easy, tasty ways to get more protein and keep things fun.</p>


<div id="recipe"></div><h2 class="feast-recipe-heading">📖 Recipe</h2><div id="wprm-recipe-container-2576" class="wprm-recipe-container" data-recipe-id="2576" data-servings="1"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-template-my-chic"><div class="wprm-container-float-right">
    <div class="wprm-recipe-image wprm-block-image-rounded"><img decoding="async" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: #666666;border-radius: 3px;" width="250" height="250" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20250%20250'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-250x250 size-250x250" alt="Close-up of oven-baked Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake with a spoonful showing rich, fudgy texture and moist interior." data-lazy-srcset="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-360x360.jpg 360w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-720x720.jpg 720w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-180x180.jpg 180w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-96x96.jpg 96w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" data-lazy-src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-360x360.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: #666666;border-radius: 3px;" width="250" height="250" src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-360x360.jpg" class="attachment-250x250 size-250x250" alt="Close-up of oven-baked Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake with a spoonful showing rich, fudgy texture and moist interior." srcset="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-360x360.jpg 360w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-720x720.jpg 720w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-180x180.jpg 180w, https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/oven-baked-high-protein-brownie-recipe-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></noscript></div>
