<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<span class="wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-author wprm-block-text-light"><a href="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/about-me/" target="_self">Jessica Stroup</a></span>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">This incredible Protein Chocolate Brownie Mug Cake is rich, fudgy, and packed with 32 grams protein per serving. Ready in just 1minute in the microwave or baked in the oven for a more traditional texture, it's a quick, high-protein, guilt-free dessert you'll love.</span></div>
