		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://healthywithachanceofsprinkles.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
This brownie mug cake was so rich and yummy. Totally satisfying. I loved it.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-1462' data-commentid="1462" data-postid="2543" data-belowelement="article-comment-1462" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Scarlet" aria-label='Reply to Scarlet'>Reply</a></div>
		
